    "description": "Normal SHMUP is a strange shoot em' up game based around classic gameplay. Go back to the roots of gameplay and defeat the cycle of <u><strong>repetition </strong></u>that plagues you. Relive memories of space invaders and other classic top down shmups. Accept the challenge of this world and defeat your own weakness now!<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Bullet hell bosses<br></li><li>Long bullet hell levels, full of a myriad of enemies<br></li><li>Three different rare power ups to boost your chances of defeating your enemies<br></li><li>5 different Bosses for 5 different levels?<br></li><li>9 unique enemies to shoot up</li></ul><br><strong>NORMAL MODE</strong><br>Contains health pickups and your health starts at 5<br><br><strong>HARDCORE MODE</strong><br>No health pickups and your health starts at 1. Get hit once and you're dead!<br><br><strong>ENDLESS MODE</strong><br>Fight through a randomly generated series of enemies. Normal mode rules apply<br><br><strong>Story</strong><br><i><u>You're pathetic aren't you?</u></i><br><br><strong>Controller</strong><br>Game has full controller support. <br>Move using the left stick and shoot using the X button or equivalent on your controller. <br>You can rebind the controller in the gamecontrollerdb.txt file.<br><br><strong>Leaderboards</strong><br>Compete for the highscore in leaderboards for all three gamemodes!",
